1593
01:33:50.776 --> 01:33:52.244
Whoa!

1594
01:33:59.319 --> 01:34:01.654
Okay! Whoa! Whoa!

1595
01:34:01.788 --> 01:34:04.790
Hey. hey. hey. hey! Listen.
