1598
01:34:12.731 --> 01:34:14.198
<b>- [ROARS]
- [JOEL GRUNTS]</b>

1599
01:34:14.333 --> 01:34:16.469
<b>- [JANICE SCREAMING]
- Oh. no!</b>

1600
01:34:16.601 --> 01:34:20.072
