1601
01:34:22.174 --> 01:34:24.276
<b>[GROANS]</b>

1602
01:34:24.810 --> 01:34:26.346
- Joel!
- Aimee!

1603
01:34:26.479 --> 01:34:29.582
Aimee! Aimee. throw me the cannon!
I know how to kill it!

1604
01:34:31.249 --> 01:34:33.352
<b>[JOEL SHOUTING]</b>

1605
01:34:36.789 --> 01:34:38.091
<b>[ROARING STOPS]</b>

1606
01:34:39.191 --> 01:34:41.060
<b>[ELECTRICAL CHARGE ZAPS]</b>

1607
01:34:41.192 --> 01:34:42.729
<b>[CRAB GROANS]</b>

1608
01:34:47.833 --> 01:34:49.502
<b>[GROANS QUIETLY]</b>

1609
01:34:49.635 --> 01:34:51.905
You can always tell in the eyes.

1610
01:34:52.038 --> 01:34:55.341
- What are you doing? Shoot it!
- Shoot it! What are you waiting for?

1611
01:34:55.475 --> 01:34:58.611
<b>- JANICE: Kill it!
- BILL: Goddamn it. shoot it!</b>

1612
01:34:59.912 --> 01:35:01.146
Needle through water.

1613
01:35:01.280 --> 01:35:03.249
<b>[CANNON FIRES]</b>

1614
01:35:04.650 --> 01:35:05.951
Cap?

1615
01:35:06.084 --> 01:35:08.787
<b>[SWITCH CLICKING]</b>

